            """
            async function() {
                window.pui.triggerSearch("garbage");
                await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1500)); // TODO: await el in humane
            }
            """
        Then There should be no logs
        Then The selector ".pagefind-ui__message" should contain "garbage is oh no"
